Class BaseProtocol.InstanceLogObject

    public static class BaseProtocol.InstanceLogObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Reserved for internal use. Write a message to the log. Log messages are comma-separated fields of the format: "local_timestamp,local_event_number,address,classname,name,MESSAGE" Where MESSAGE is the result of String.format(formatStr,arguments).
